<inglise> - their conformity with the objectives referred to in paragraph 1, </inglise>
<eesti> - nende vastavust l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud eesm&auml;rkidele, </eesti>
<inglise> - their conformity with the eligibility criteria laid down in Article 3, </inglise>
<eesti> - nende vastavust artiklis 3 nimetatud toetusk&otilde;lblikkuse kriteeriumidele, </eesti>
<inglise> - their Community interest, taking account of the common transport policy, </inglise>
