<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The projects or measures shall be eligible for financial assistance from the Community provided they are financed wholly or in part by public authorities and can be shown to be of Community interest in terms of the following criteria: </inglise>
